  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to validate a feasible, safe and reliable iohexol plasma
      clearance method in routine monitoring of the renal function (GFR) in children.

      Different parameters of renal function will be compared to the gold standard multiple sample
      points procedure of iohexol clearance.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
